        📄 The Lion Sleeps Tonight – Guitar
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="/downloads/The_Lion_Sleeps_Tonight-Bass.pdf"
        download
        class="cta-button"
      >
        📄 The Lion Sleeps Tonight – Bass
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a
        href="https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1-mo63I6v5hePqOrrbJqEz6w1PaiI8NH0"
